{"tid":1539742,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［要唔要改口號］四大訴求定五大訴求？","createTime":"2019-09-04T10:19:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T10:22:01.000Z","uid":47719,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"aa2a72f512c53d5a162d896bc97f5f48f29f81d0","tid":1539742,"uid":47719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:19:31.000Z","msg":"四大訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n五大訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c45f223be894fc1eac5b8709dd79a08c6e8ab1f","tid":1539742,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:20:25.000Z","msg":"大家要到幾時先察覺，靠政府去實現五大訴求已經變成一個好恐怖既局？<br />\n<br />\n[時光倒流Re-post] 香港民權抗爭&mdash;&mdash;五大訴求，缺一不可？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538204\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538204</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先大家可以選擇服用咗以上文章先<br />\n<br />\n然後我可以反問一句，有冇人諗過五大訴求真係實現既情況會係點？<br />\n<br />\n係，的確可能證實到瘋狂既民意係可以改變到政府所作出既決定，但下次兩地一檢呢？再下次智慧燈柱、全面普教中呢？反送中2.0、3.0發生，真係好？點解要跟住個垃圾政權條尾走？<br />\n<br />\n香港人，唔好再「<span style=\"color: red;\">要求</span>」政府畀到五個願望你哋，請大家一齊親手達成依五個，甚至一百個願望都得，可唔可以？<br />\n<br />\n睇唔明我講咩既話請讀上面篇文章一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05f90f160ef146f675e9dd056d3ff73f761b62f2","tid":1539742,"uid":214662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:20:44.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 下一句係咩？"},{"pid":"66e51208f109eae8653d15aeed793020ff759a50","tid":1539742,"uid":4108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:20:45.000Z","msg":"釋出善意，四大訴求"},{"pid":"a01e4966b9f5a10155c62c2129979672300c0e72","tid":1539742,"uid":47719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:21:59.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 呢句口號不能改<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1539573\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1539573</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"05786459abc22d07d1cb3396ef21365037b9a1c7","tid":1539742,"uid":186,"l